name:               cedict
version:            0.2.5
category:           Text
description:        Convenient Chinese phrase & character lookup.
synopsis:           Convenient Chinese phrase & character lookup.
license:            GPL
license-file:       LICENSE
author:             Jason Dusek
maintainer:         jason.dusek@gmail.com
